       "&gt;&gt;&gt; model = TFPreTrainedModel.from_pretrained(\"some_folder\")\n",
       "```===== Document 5 =====\n",
       "# Saving the Model\n",
       "\n",
       "All TensorFlow models in 🤗 Transformers have a method named\n",
